                     <interp inst="t17730707-56-person567" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a bricklayer: Levi was my <rs id="t17730707-56-deflabel289" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17730707-56-defend561 t17730707-56-deflabel289"></join>. Hearing of this lead, I questioned him about it in the morning; he said he found it in Mrs. King's garden; we afterwards went and compared the lead with the place the lead was cut from, and it tallied exactly with the place.</p>
               <p>- Mitcham, the constable, confirms the evidence<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177307070050"></xptr> of the lead being the same that was found upon the prisoner.</p>
